```
String[] values = { "Java ", null, "", "is ", "great!" };
String result = "";

for (String value : values) {
    result = result + value;
}
```

```
for (String value : values) {
    result = result + (value == null ? "" : value);
}

assertEquals("Java is great!", result);
```

